        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="资源网站"><a href="#资源网站" class="headerlink" title="资源网站"></a>资源网站</h1><p><strong>只因知道了这15个神级网站，就能白嫖全世界资源!照片&#x2F;壁纸&#x2F;AI语音&#x2F;音频视频素材&#x2F;图标&#x2F;插画&#x2F;字体&#x2F;电子书&#x2F;画作&#x2F;地图</strong></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614001.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614001.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><h2 id="照片"><a href="#照片" class="headerlink" title="照片"></a><strong>照片</strong></h2><p>1、Unsplash：<a href="https://unsplash.com/">https://unsplash.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614694.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614694.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071603263.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071603263.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614461.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614461.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p>只支持英文进行搜索</p><p>2、pixabay：<a href="https://pixabay.com/zh/">https://pixabay.com/zh/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615377.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615377.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615594.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615594.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><h2 id="壁纸"><a href="#壁纸" class="headerlink" title="壁纸"></a><strong>壁纸</strong></h2><p>0、Wallpaper Engine</p><p>在steam商城下载（收费）</p><p>1、wallhaven：<a href="https://wallhaven.cc/">https://wallhaven.cc/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615642.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615642.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p>2、极简壁纸：<a href="https://bz.zzzmh.cn/">https://bz.zzzmh.cn/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556732.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556732.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p>国内的网站，全部的资源来源于上一个网站，访问速度更快，界面简洁。</p><h2 id="AI语音"><a href="#AI语音" class="headerlink" title="AI语音"></a><strong>AI语音</strong></h2><p>1、微软Azure项目：<a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-cn/products/cognitive-services/text-to-speech/#overview">https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-cn/products/cognitive-services/text-to-speech/#overview</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556768.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556768.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><h2 id="音频-x2F-视频素材"><a href="#音频-x2F-视频素材" class="headerlink" title="音频&#x2F;视频素材"></a><strong>音频&#x2F;视频素材</strong></h2><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556688.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556688.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p>1、哔哩哔哩：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/">https://www.bilibili.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071603031.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071603031.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556532.jpeg" alt="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556532.jpeg"></p><p>img</p><h2 id="图标-x2F-插画"><a href="#图标-x2F-插画" class="headerlink" title="图标&#x2F;插画"></a><strong>图标&#x2F;插画</strong></h2><p>1、iconfont：<a href="https://www.iconfont.cn/">https://www.iconfont.cn/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556159.jpeg" alt="https://z